I want to post this now so we can start planning I know Ugod may be planning to make a presence I would like to assist if at all possible Please add any ne warning signs to this tread.  This information comes to use from '1st of light' guild and their excelent work.  My guess is halloween like Kith last year.  Look for more information here www.1fol.cjb.net<br>
